    "plan_content": "The plan is ready for your review. Here's a quick summary:\n\n**What we're building:** A new `@ai-sdk/pixelart` package at `packages/pixelart/` that implements an image-only AI provider.\n\n**12 files to create**, modeled closely after `@ai-sdk/black-forest-labs` (the closest existing image-only provider):\n- **Config files** (6): `package.json`, `tsconfig.json`, `tsconfig.build.json`, `tsup.config.ts`, `turbo.json`, vitest configs\n- **Source files** (5): `version.ts`, `pixelart-image-settings.ts`, `pixelart-image-model.ts`, `pixelart-provider.ts`, `index.ts`\n\n**Key design decisions:**\n- Synchronous API (POST → base64 images), simpler than BFL's polling model\n- Provider options (`style`, `pixelDensity`) validated via `parseProviderOptions` with the `lazySchema`/`zodSchema` pattern for zod v3/v4 compat\n- `NoSuchModelError` thrown for language/embedding model requests\n- Auth via `Authorization: Bearer` header, API key from `PIXELART_API_KEY` env var\n- Warns on unsupported features (`files`, `mask`, `aspectRatio`)",
